Gaga [[Lilongwe]] ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 6 idas 6 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. 
Manu ka dxgal Malawi ga wada sugan 59.20%  ka dxgal qpahan, 34% ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 6.80% na.

